before security broke up the problems.
</P>
<P>
   A no-tolerance policy will be in effect for Tuesday night's
game, and spotters will be in the stands watching for possible
problems. Anyone causing any trouble will be ejected, might be
subject to arrest and could have their ticket privileges revoked,
the release warned.
